{
  "description": "A vibrant blue bird perched on a branch heavily covered in pale green lichen, amidst a network of bare, twisting branches. The lichen creates a textured, almost fractal pattern across the branches. Small patches of orange fungal growth are scattered throughout the lichen, adding subtle contrast. The bird is facing left, its blue plumage bright against the muted tones of the branches. The depth of field is shallow, focusing on the bird and nearby branches, with the background blurred. The light is diffused, creating a soft and natural illumination.",
